<P>
SAN DIEGO COUNTY DIGEST 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Police have arrested two suspects in the fatal shooting Friday night of a 
teen-ager at Martin Luther King Park in Southeast San Diego. 
</P>
<P>
