SHOOTINGS -- ISRAEL; ISRAEL -- ARMED FORCES; ISRAEL -- TERRITORIES AND 
POSSESSIONS; PALESTINIANS -- ISRAEL; WEST BANK (ISRAEL); GAZA STRIP 
</P>
