<P>
QUAKE SHAKES AUSTRIA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
VIENNA 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A "moderately strong" earth tremor, with a magnitude of 4.5, shook buildings in 
Austria's mountainous northern Tyrol region early Sunday but caused no damage, 
a spokesman for Vienna's meteorological institute said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
